  "instructions": [
    "Preheat grill to medium-high heat.",
    "Thread sausage pieces, onion, and bell pepper (if using) onto skewers.",
    "Brush skewers with olive oil and season with salt and pepper.",
    "Grill skewers for 8-10 minutes, turning occasionally.",
    "Meanwhile, prepare the fiery glaze by combining all ingredients in a saucepan.",
    "Bring the glaze to a boil over medium heat, then reduce heat to low and simmer for 5 minutes.",
    "Brush the glaze over the kebabs during the last 2 minutes of grilling.",
    "Serve hot and enjoy!"
